title: IT COMES FROM BELOW | BRYCE HARPER
description:
Baseball is a numbers game. No one knows this better than Bryce Harper. But just remember, no number sounds as good as the crack of a bat.

transcripts: Look baseball's a number game, a 570 foot home run at age 15, 31 homers in 66 games, first front cover at 16, number one overall draft pick, majors at 19, over a hundred home runs as 34 on base percentage 340, then 368, then 460, four-time all-star meeting 9.2 million balance. 30 out of 30 MVP votes, chasing 716, 4256, 2297, 3562, 220 at age 23, but kid just remember no number sounds as good as this.
